    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It runs smoothly, the interior is nice and comfy, and it still looks great parked in the driveway! If you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
