    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman that perfectly embodies the spirit of a true driver's car. The exterior is finished in a striking Guards Red that still holds a deep, mirror-like gloss. While the body is straight and free of any major blemishes, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and lower rockers\u2014honest evidence of spirited weekend drives. Inside, the cabin remains a focused and comfortable environment; the black leather sport seats are in excellent shape, showing only slight softening on the entry bolster. All interior electronics, including the PCM navigation and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the turbocharged boxer engine pulls strongly through the entire rev range, paired with a crisp-shifting transmission. This vehicle comes with a comprehensive service folder, including a recent major interval service and a fresh set of high-performance tires. It has been garage-kept and non-smoked in, offering the next owner a turn-key experience with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 36500.0,
